&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to recruit caring, compassionate, experienced mental health staff nurses to provide high quality care to our patients.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;As one of the leading trusts in clinical excellence, we provide you with excellent personal and career development opportunities and offer you an enhanced rate for your services in line with the agenda for change framework.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful candidates will be able to demonstrate that they can make positive contributions to the team, provide safe, effective, personalised care and strive to achieve the RFH ‘world class care values’. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The trust operates its own extremely active staff bank and provides excellent clinical and educational opportunities for registered mental health nurses to gain a wide range of experience throughout all departments. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This is an ideal opportunity for highly motivated, enthusiastic, forward thinking nurses to gain or maintain clinical competencies whilst experiencing ultimate work life balance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Temporary Staffing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: rf.tsrecruitment@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 0207 794 0500 EXT 23400&lt;/p&gt;
